# Employee Leave Management System

A full-stack web application to digitize employee leave approval process, built with Django, Django REST Framework, and MySQL.

## Features
- Employee Management (Add/View/Update/Delete)
- Leave Management (Apply/View/Edit/Delete) with status tracking (Pending/Approved/Rejected)
- Dashboard with live counts (Total Employees, Total Leaves, Pending, Approved, Rejected)
- Search employees by Name or Employee ID
- Filter leaves by Status and Leave Type
- REST APIs for Employee and Leave modules (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
- User Authentication (Login/Logout) with protected views and APIs
- Pagination on Employee and Leave lists
- Bootstrap-based responsive UI

## Tech Stack
- Python 3, Django, Django REST Framework
- MySQL Database
- HTML, CSS, Bootstrap 5
- Git & GitHub

